\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"169\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"Quy t\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u 60-30-10 gi\\\\u00fap c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng kh\\\\u00f4ng gian\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"2u75i\\\\\\\"></p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"cach-tan-dung-hieu-ung-mau-sac-dje-mo-rong-hoac-thu-nho-khong-gian\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"u3942\\\\\\\"><b>C\\\\u00e1ch t\\\\u1eadn d\\\\u1ee5ng hi\\\\u1ec7u \\\\u1ee9ng m\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc \\\\u0111\\\\u1ec3 m\\\\u1edf r\\\\u1ed9ng ho\\\\u1eb7c thu nh\\\\u1ecf kh\\\\u00f4ng gian</b></h3><ul><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"3ctt3\\\\\\\">M\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u00e1ng (tr\\\\u1eafng, kem, pastel): Gi\\\\u00fap kh\\\\u00f4ng gian r\\\\u1ed9ng r\\\\u00e3i, tho\\\\u00e1ng \\\\u0111\\\\u00e3ng.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"4hse7\\\\\\\">M\\\\u00e0u t\\\\u1ed1i (x\\\\u00e1m \\\\u0111\\\\u1eadm, xanh navy): T\\\\u1ea1o c\\\\u1ea3m gi\\\\u00e1c \\\\u1ea5m c\\\\u00fang, sang tr\\\\u1ecdng.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"e0cnt\\\\\\\">M\\\\u00e0u trung t\\\\u00ednh (x\\\\u00e1m, n\\\\u00e2u nh\\\\u1ea1t): \\\\u0110\\\\u1ea3m b\\\\u1ea3o s\\\\u1ef1 c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng, th\\\\u01b0 th\\\\u00e1i.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"2qt7n\\\\\\\">Ngo\\\\u00e0i ra, tr\\\\u1ea7n s\\\\u00e1ng h\\\\u01a1n t\\\\u01b0\\\\u1eddng s\\\\u1ebd gi\\\\u00fap ph\\\\u00f2ng tr\\\\u00f4ng cao h\\\\u01a1n, ng\\\\u01b0\\\\u1ee3c l\\\\u1ea1i, tr\\\\u1ea7n t\\\\u1ed1i h\\\\u01a1n t\\\\u1ea1o c\\\\u1ea3m gi\\\\u00e1c g\\\\u1ea7n g\\\\u0169i.</p><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"eql9a\\\\\\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"170\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"L\\\\u1ef1a ch\\\\u1ecdn m\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u00f9 h\\\\u1ee3p gi\\\\u00fap t\\\\u1ea1o kh\\\\u00f4ng gian r\\\\u1ed9ng r\\\\u00e3i, \\\\u1ea5m c\\\\u00fang v\\\\u00e0 c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng cho ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7.\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"fptkr\\\\\\\"></p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"nhung-loi-phoi-mau-pho-bien-khien-phong-ngu-kem-tham-my\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"3d17k\\\\\\\"><b>Nh\\\\u1eefng l\\\\u1ed7i ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u1ed5 bi\\\\u1ebfn khi\\\\u1ebfn ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 k\\\\u00e9m th\\\\u1ea9m m\\\\u1ef9</b></h3><ul><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"f9lna\\\\\\\">D\\\\u00f9ng qu\\\\u00e1 nhi\\\\u1ec1u m\\\\u00e0u r\\\\u1ef1c r\\\\u1ee1: Khi\\\\u1ebfn kh\\\\u00f4ng gian tr\\\\u1edf n\\\\u00ean n\\\\u1eb7ng n\\\\u1ec1, r\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u1eaft.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"79m73\\\\\\\">Thi\\\\u1ebfu s\\\\u1ef1 c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng: Kh\\\\u00f4ng tu\\\\u00e2n th\\\\u1ee7 nguy\\\\u00ean t\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u khi\\\\u1ebfn ph\\\\u00f2ng m\\\\u1ea5t \\\\u0111i s\\\\u1ef1 h\\\\u00e0i h\\\\u00f2a.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"a7gcq\\\\\\\">Ch\\\\u1ec9 d\\\\u00f9ng m\\\\u1ed9t m\\\\u00e0u: D\\\\u1ec5 khi\\\\u1ebfn kh\\\\u00f4ng gian \\\\u0111\\\\u01a1n \\\\u0111i\\\\u1ec7u, thi\\\\u1ebfu s\\\\u1ee9c s\\\\u1ed1ng.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"bg0f6\\\\\\\">B\\\\u1ecf qua y\\\\u1ebfu t\\\\u1ed1 \\\\u00e1nh s\\\\u00e1ng: \\\\u00c1nh s\\\\u00e1ng c\\\\u00f3 th\\\\u1ec3 thay \\\\u0111\\\\u1ed5i s\\\\u1eafc \\\\u0111\\\\u1ed9 m\\\\u00e0u, c\\\\u1ea7n c\\\\u00e2n nh\\\\u1eafc k\\\\u1ef9 khi l\\\\u1ef1a ch\\\\u1ecdn.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"ft3tv\\\\\\\">Vi\\\\u1ec7c tr\\\\u00e1nh nh\\\\u1eefng sai l\\\\u1ea7m n\\\\u00e0y gi\\\\u00fap ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 v\\\\u1eeba \\\\u0111\\\\u1eb9p v\\\\u1eeba t\\\\u1ea1o c\\\\u1ea3m gi\\\\u00e1c th\\\\u01b0 gi\\\\u00e3n t\\\\u1ed1i \\\\u0111a.</p><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"24kdc\\\\\\\"></p><h2 id=\\\\\\\"goi-y-bang-mau-phoi-hop-cho-phong-ngu-theo-phong-cach-thiet-ke\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"ekgwv\\\\\\\"><b>G\\\\u1ee3i \\\\u00fd b\\\\u1ea3ng m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u1ed1i h\\\\u1ee3p cho ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 theo phong c\\\\u00e1ch thi\\\\u1ebft k\\\\u1ebf</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"ghto\\\\\\\">M\\\\u1ed7i phong c\\\\u00e1ch thi\\\\u1ebft k\\\\u1ebf n\\\\u1ed9i th\\\\u1ea5t mang m\\\\u1ed9t n\\\\u00e9t \\\\u0111\\\\u1eb7c tr\\\\u01b0ng ri\\\\u00eang, th\\\\u1ec3 hi\\\\u1ec7n qua c\\\\u00e1ch ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 h\\\\u00e0i h\\\\u00f2a gi\\\\u1eefa th\\\\u1ea9m m\\\\u1ef9 v\\\\u00e0 c\\\\u00f4ng n\\\\u0103ng.</p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"phoi-mau-phong-ngu-phong-cach-toi-gian-(minimalist)\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"asr2j\\\\\\\"><b>Ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch t\\\\u1ed1i gi\\\\u1ea3n (Minimalist)</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"4gii6\\\\\\\">Minimalist chu\\\\u1ed9ng b\\\\u1ea3ng m\\\\u00e0u trung t\\\\u00ednh, tinh gi\\\\u1ea3n nh\\\\u01b0ng v\\\\u1eabn tinh t\\\\u1ebf:</p><ul><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"ai9ev\\\\\\\">Tr\\\\u1eafng - X\\\\u00e1m - Be: Nh\\\\u1eb9 nh\\\\u00e0ng, thanh l\\\\u1ecbch, gi\\\\u00fap m\\\\u1edf r\\\\u1ed9ng kh\\\\u00f4ng gian.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"9c3n2\\\\\\\">X\\\\u00e1m - Tr\\\\u1eafng - \\\\u0110en: C\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng gi\\\\u1eefa hi\\\\u1ec7n \\\\u0111\\\\u1ea1i v\\\\u00e0 t\\\\u1ed1i gi\\\\u1ea3n, ph\\\\u00f9 h\\\\u1ee3p v\\\\u1edbi ng\\\\u01b0\\\\u1eddi th\\\\u00edch s\\\\u1ef1 s\\\\u1eafc n\\\\u00e9t.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"dmi25\\\\\\\">N\\\\u00e2u g\\\\u1ed7 - Kem - Be: T\\\\u1ea1o c\\\\u1ea3m gi\\\\u00e1c \\\\u1ea5m \\\\u00e1p, th\\\\u01b0 th\\\\u00e1i.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"erce9\\\\\\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"171\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"L\\\\u1ef1a ch\\\\u1ecdn m\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u00f9 h\\\\u1ee3p gi\\\\u00fap t\\\\u1ea1o kh\\\\u00f4ng gian r\\\\u1ed9ng r\\\\u00e3i, \\\\u1ea5m c\\\\u00fang v\\\\u00e0 c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng cho ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7.\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"dljlf\\\\\\\"></p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"phoi-mau-phong-ngu-phong-cach-hien-djai-(modern)\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"a8mq3\\\\\\\"><b>Ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch 