: \\\\u1ea4m \\\\u00e1p, tinh t\\\\u1ebf.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"6l3cg\\\\\\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"173\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"Ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch B\\\\u1eafc \\\\u00c2u (Scandinavian)\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"kjvg\\\\\\\"></p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"mau-sac-phong-ngu-phong-cach-co-djien-(classic)\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"mfo3v\\\\\\\"><b>M\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch c\\\\u1ed5 \\\\u0111i\\\\u1ec3n (Classic)</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"5mckk\\\\\\\">T\\\\u00f4n vinh s\\\\u1ef1 sang tr\\\\u1ecdng, qu\\\\u00fd ph\\\\u00e1i v\\\\u1edbi b\\\\u1ea3ng m\\\\u00e0u thanh l\\\\u1ecbch:</p><ul><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"1hf34\\\\\\\">Kem - V\\\\u00e0ng \\\\u00e1nh kim - N\\\\u00e2u s\\\\u1eabm: Ho\\\\u00e0ng gia, \\\\u0111\\\\u1eb3ng c\\\\u1ea5p.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"6ngro\\\\\\\">\\\\u0110\\\\u1ecf r\\\\u01b0\\\\u1ee3u vang - Be - G\\\\u1ed7 \\\\u00f3c ch\\\\u00f3: \\\\u1ea4m c\\\\u00fang, quy\\\\u1ec1n l\\\\u1ef1c.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"1pv66\\\\\\\">Xanh r\\\\u00eau - V\\\\u00e0ng \\\\u0111\\\\u1ed3ng - Tr\\\\u1eafng ng\\\\u1ecdc trai: C\\\\u1ed5 \\\\u0111i\\\\u1ec3n, thanh l\\\\u1ecbch.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"atvlr\\\\\\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"174\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"M\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch c\\\\u1ed5 \\\\u0111i\\\\u1ec3n (Classic)\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"ccl7\\\\\\\"></p><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"2snsi\\\\\\\"><b>Ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch Bohemian (Boho)</b></p><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"77fm8\\\\\\\">Boho mang n\\\\u00e9t t\\\\u1ef1 do, ph\\\\u00f3ng kho\\\\u00e1ng v\\\\u1edbi c\\\\u00e1ch ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ng\\\\u1eabu h\\\\u1ee9ng:</p><ul><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"148gs\\\\\\\">Cam \\\\u0111\\\\u1ea5t - Xanh l\\\\u00e1 - N\\\\u00e2u g\\\\u1ed7: T\\\\u1ef1 nhi\\\\u00ean, \\\\u1ea5n t\\\\u01b0\\\\u1ee3ng.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"brplb\\\\\\\">H\\\\u1ed3ng \\\\u0111\\\\u1ea5t - Be - Tr\\\\u1eafng: L\\\\u00e3ng m\\\\u1ea1n, nh\\\\u1eb9 nh\\\\u00e0ng.</li><li data-block-key=\\\\\\\"frm3s\\\\\\\">V\\\\u00e0ng mustard - Xanh navy - \\\\u0110\\\\u1ecf g\\\\u1ea1ch: C\\\\u00e1 t\\\\u00ednh, ngh\\\\u1ec7 thu\\\\u1eadt.</li></ul><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"4fc94\\\\\\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\\"captioned_fullwidth\\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\\"176\\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\\"Ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 phong c\\\\u00e1ch Bohemian (Boho)\\\\\\\"/><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"7h8n0\\\\\\\"></p><h2 id=\\\\\\\"cach-phoi-mau-phong-ngu-theo-phong-thuy-va-ban-menh-gia-chu\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"fxa2v\\\\\\\"><b>C\\\\u00e1ch ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 theo phong th\\\\u1ee7y v\\\\u00e0 b\\\\u1ea3n m\\\\u1ec7nh gia ch\\\\u1ee7</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"44oda\\\\\\\">Vi\\\\u1ec7c ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 kh\\\\u00f4ng ch\\\\u1ec9 \\\\u1ea3nh h\\\\u01b0\\\\u1edfng \\\\u0111\\\\u1ebfn th\\\\u1ea9m m\\\\u1ef9 m\\\\u00e0 c\\\\u00f2n t\\\\u00e1c \\\\u0111\\\\u1ed9ng \\\\u0111\\\\u1ebfn phong th\\\\u1ee7y, gi\\\\u00fap c\\\\u00e2n b\\\\u1eb1ng n\\\\u0103ng l\\\\u01b0\\\\u1ee3ng v\\\\u00e0 mang l\\\\u1ea1i t\\\\u00e0i l\\\\u1ed9c, b\\\\u00ecnh an. D\\\\u01b0\\\\u1edbi \\\\u0111\\\\u00e2y l\\\\u00e0 g\\\\u1ee3i \\\\u00fd ph\\\\u1ed1i m\\\\u00e0u theo t\\\\u1eebng b\\\\u1ea3n m\\\\u1ec7nh.</p><h3 id=\\\\\\\"mau-sac-phong-ngu-hop-menh-kim\\\\\\\" data-block-key=\\\\\\\"9jsom\\\\\\\"><b>M\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u1eafc ph\\\\u00f2ng ng\\\\u1ee7 h\\\\u1ee3p m\\\\u1ec7nh Kim</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\\\\\\"c4h4r\\\\\\\">Gia ch\\\\u1ee7 m\\\\u1ec7nh Kim n\\\\u00ean ch\\\\u1ecdn c\\\\u00e1c t\\\\u00f4ng m\\\\u00e0u s\\\\u00e1ng nh\\\\u01b0 tr\\\\u1eafng, x\\\\u00e1m, be, v\